notable_aspects.interpretation: Heightened communication and insight; clarity of thought.
Emotional renewal, depth of feeling, subconscious empowerment.
Creative harmony between desire and action.

matches.detail: The Hermit's guidance in the Past and Ten of Pentacles' manifestation in the Future support The Lovers' reversed message in the Present.
matches.why: Integration of emotional truth with practical progress

tensions.detail: The Lovers' reversal may indicate inner turmoil or self-doubt, which can be addressed through introspection and self-compassion.

interpretation.theme: Integration of emotional truth with practical progress
action_items: Choose one recovery habit (sleep/walk/quiet time) and track it daily for 7 days.
Set a daily stop-time and honor it 5 days this week.
Say no to one nonessential request to protect focus.
Time-block two 90-minute deep-work sessions on your calendar for the next 7 days.
Define one 30-day goal; break it into 4 weekly deliverables and schedule the first.
Turn off one recurring distraction during deep-work windows (notifications, tabs, chat).
List one commitment to release and notify stakeholders within 48 hours.
Timebox work blocks and rest blocks on your calendar for the next 7 days.
Pair one emotional truth with one practical step and schedule it this week.
affirmations: I am worthy of love and success.

confidence.notes: The Full Moon energy highlights the importance of release, balance, and integration.
